snippet.title: RetroRealms Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Pre-order the RETROREALMS: HALLOWEEN COLLECTOR'S EDITION here! - https://retrorealmsgame.com/collectors-edition/

Boss Team Games and WayForward announce RetroRealms: Halloween and RetroRealms: Ash vs Evil Dead!
